 DEFINE OUTPUT PARAMETER pcToolbars AS CHARACTER  NO-UNDO.

 DEFINE VARIABLE htype AS HANDLE     NO-UNDO.
 DEFINE VARIABLE hObj  AS HANDLE     NO-UNDO.

